{"tid":762612,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺食m記自己收餐盤班人好虛偽兼無腦？（左膠+未打過工child勿入）","createTime":"2018-07-31T12:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T23:06:41.000Z","uid":102240,"like":9,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5864d0ee926f66e4350c21c387bff96ef6717193","tid":762612,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:13:45.000Z","msg":"扮外國人收餐盤懶有手尾但就害到人無工開<br />\n<br />\n我當平均m記一個鐘做40個客，有一半係堂食，每人用一隻餐盤<br />\n<br />\n20*24=480隻餐廳要人盤，我當收一個餐盤要1分鐘<span style=\"color: red;\">（實有傻仔話收餐盤可以一次過唔駛咁耐，麻煩用你個垃圾腦諗下d人唔係一次過食晒個餐，要巡要等）</span>，簡單唔計ot一個員工返8個鐘，即係一更m記要額外請6個人黎收盤，雖然m記就唔會特別開個人黎收盤，無左餐盤呢樣野就少6個人有工開，我估大大話話香港都有百幾間m記？成千人隨時因為你果班懶醒去收盤既左膠無工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1c8c32a8a91e783533faf311026f37da3ad0ed","tid":762612,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:16:56.000Z","msg":"1分鐘唔夠<br />\n因為仲要消毒"},{"pid":"0539a24fee3daefd29cc07ca82096ad6dcc6477b","tid":762612,"uid":17606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:17:39.000Z","msg":"其實樓主係我表妹<br />\n佢細細個已經食G唔食皮 食橙食橙皮"},{"pid":"09bf7475171f0f55e6fa5713f0ca151d2587f214","tid":762612,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0539a24fee3daefd29cc07ca82096ad6dcc6477b","tid":762612,"uid":17606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:17:39.000Z","msg":"其實樓主係我表妹<br />\n佢細細個已經食G唔食皮 食橙食橙皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"你up乜啊"},{"pid":"99c6ecc465965035d2258baf7dcf2c8ae4917cd7","tid":762612,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"咩咩妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9b9c08dfcd98d82d2ca4dc3e730b1f29fba97b","tid":762612,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"好似好有道理<br />\n事實係為自己懶既習慣搵藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"